scode False {'lang': 'rust'}
codeb
    let node1 = Node {val:10,  tail: None};
    let mut node2 = Node {val: 10, tail: None};
    node2.val = 15; 
bedoc

The mutability qualifier applies all the fields in the struct.  Trying to change a field of 
scode
node1
edoc
